  "description": "High crystallinity, minimal depth. The obsidian sheet is very thin here — almost translucent. Low resonance means the chime rings once and departs, not accumulates. Imagine chimes heard from the garden, two rooms away: bright but gentle, each strike its own small moment. Safe for children who love shimmer.",
